annotation.text:
Description: This process governs the activity of the customer's user with admin rights or CST officers to authorise the user requesting access to a customer account.
Pre-conditions: - User row has been created in Connect DB and has status Enabled. - User_Application row is not created yet in Connect DB. * UPDATE 20150928: User_Application is now checked and updated if existing, created if new (Status was Pending)
Post conditions: - User_Application row is created/updated in Connect DB. - User_Role_Map row is created in Connect DB. - Letter of approval/refusal is generated and persisted in Connect DB. - Distribution email is created, sent and persisted in Connect DB.
